00:25:59.140 --> 00:26:03.940
So I want to make the point now that while
a corporation is always a super organism.

00:26:03.940 --> 00:26:08.580
In fact, the legal definition of a corporation,
going back to eighteenth century Dutch and

00:26:08.580 --> 00:26:13.049
British law, is a group of people united into
one body.

00:26:13.049 --> 00:26:16.240
The word corporation literally means body.

00:26:16.240 --> 00:26:19.880
So Mitt Romney is not entirely wrong when
he says corporations are people, although

00:26:19.880 --> 00:26:24.000
of course, it they are people they are a certain
kind of person that does not have much in

00:26:24.000 --> 00:26:25.650
the way of moral sentiments in and of itself.

00:26:25.650 --> 00:26:27.540
But we won't go there.

00:26:27.540 --> 00:26:35.550
Alright, so, a corporation is always a super
organism, it is a kind of emergent entity.

00:26:35.550 --> 00:26:38.180
But I want to make it clear, I'm not saying
that they are hives, most are not.

00:26:38.180 --> 00:26:39.550
Very few are hives.

00:26:39.550 --> 00:26:43.270
There's a dimension of hivishness and even
within the same industry.

00:26:43.270 --> 00:26:47.842
So, here are some companies just from my limited
experience in the business world around or

00:26:47.842 --> 00:26:50.640
rather just teaching courses to people in
