00:29:20.400 --> 00:29:21.910
and works as a team.

00:29:21.910 --> 00:29:23.429
So you get lower turnover.

00:29:23.429 --> 00:29:26.240
Turnover is extremely expensive for companies.

00:29:26.240 --> 00:29:29.880
And when people are fired, or when they leave
