00:29:37.730 --> 00:29:38.730
them away.

00:29:38.730 --> 00:29:42.179
So hivishness has obvious benefits for companies.

00:29:42.179 --> 00:29:46.760
Now it also surely has downsides and it depends
how you do it, so I'm not standing here saying

00:29:46.760 --> 00:29:48.360
"Oh, every company should become more hivish."

00:29:48.360 --> 00:29:50.270
I have no idea if that's true.

00:29:50.270 --> 00:29:51.590
But I do want to introduce these terms.

00:29:51.590 --> 00:29:56.000
I think it's helpful for people in the business
world to think about.

00:29:56.000 --> 00:30:00.600
So possible risks or downsides are at a certain
