00:30:20.860 --> 00:30:22.360
of toxic for outsiders.

00:30:22.360 --> 00:30:28.090
You could no longer care about other stake
holders, other people outside the company.

00:30:28.090 --> 00:30:31.930
Of course, if you have more group loyalty
