cognition is that it's recursive.

00:45:29.200 --> 00:45:33.849
So there's this Arab proverb: "Me against
my brother, me and my brother against our

00:45:33.849 --> 00:45:36.479
cousin, me and my brother and cousin against
the stranger."

00:45:36.479 --> 00:45:40.079
