compete within a patrol; they'll then cooperate

00:45:49.499 --> 00:45:52.670
to compete against the next patrol and all
the way up until the Marines are competing

00:45:52.670 --> 00:45:53.670
against the Navy.

00:45:53.670 --> 00:45:59.109
And then of course in war, the whole US Military
is competing against another military organization.

00:45:59.109 --> 00:46:04.619
So, there is no limit to how high we can go
as long as there's someone on the other side.

00:46:04.619 --> 00:46:09.529
